				h2 04-06/2011 &mdash; Ninja Marketing
				h4 Editor

			.story-block-body
				p The Design Section introduced a big change in NM's marketing-centric tradition; as an editor I was given the task of launching the new section, establishing an editorial line, and recruiting a team of contributors. #[a(href='http://www.ninjamarketing.it/2011/04/19/ninja-marketing-speaks-design-al-via-la-nuova-sezione-dedicata-alle-arti-visive-a-tutto-tondo/', target='_blank') &rarr; read my post for the launch of Ninja Marketing Design (in Italian)]

		.story-block
